enny |last=Mielke|language=German}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2015\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|  \n| rowspan=\"7\"| ''Ich bin ein Berliner''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Ich bin ein Berliner\"<ref name=\"ib1b\">{{cite web |url=https://hiphop.de/release/ufo361-ich-bin-ein-berliner |title=Ufo361 \u2013 Ich bin ein Berliner |publisher=HipHop.de |accessdate=24 June 2018 |language=German}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|  \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Allein\"<ref name=\"ib1b\" />\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|  \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Harman\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://hiphop.de/video/ufo361-video-zu-harman-heizt-label-geruechte-an |title=Ufo361: Video zu \"Harman\" heizt Label-Ger\u00fcchte an |publisher=HipHop.de |date=22 December 2015 |accessdate=24 June 2018 |first=Clark |last=Senger |language=German}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|  \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Scottie Pippen\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.backspin.de/ufo361-scottie-pippen/ |title=Ufo361 \u2013 \u201eScottie Pippen\u201c an |publisher=Backspin |date=19 February 2016 |accessdate=24 June 2018|language=German}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"7\"| 2016\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|  \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"BLNFFM\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://hiphop.de/video/ufo361-ft-celo-abdi-blnffm |title=Ufo361 ft. Celo & Abdi \u2013 BLNFFM |publisher=HipHop.de |date=13 March 2016 |first=Karo |last=Hellmich  |accessdate=24 June 2018|language=German}}</ref><br /><small>(featuring Celo & Abdi)</small>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|  \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Ich bin ein Berliner Remix\"<ref>{{cite web |url=https://hiphop.de/video/ufo361-liefert-ich-bin-ein-berliner-remix-mit-sido-bass-sultan-hengzt-btng-crackaveli |title=Ufo361 liefert \"Ich bin ein Berliner\"-Remix mit Sido, Bass Sultan Hengzt, BTNG & Crackaveli |publisher=HipHop.de |date=24 March 2016 |first=Karo |last=Hellmich |accessdate=24 June 2018|language=German}}</ref><br /><small>(featuring [[Sido (rapper)|Sido]], Bass Sultan Hengzt, BTNG & Crackaveli)<