tcharts\">{{cite web |url=http://www.austriancharts.at/search.asp?search=UFO361&cat=s |title=Austrian Discography \u2013 Ufo361 |publisher=[[\u00d63 Austria Top 40]] |accessdate=24 October 2018 |language=German}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:2.5em; font-size:85%\" rowspan=\"2\"| [[Swiss Hitparade|SWI]]<br /><ref name=\"swicharts\">{{cite web |url=http://hitparade.ch/search.asp?search=UFO361&cat=s|title=Swiss Discography \u2013 Ufo361 |publisher=[[Swiss Hitparade]] |accessdate=24 October 2018 |language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n! style=\"width:2.5em; font-size:85%\"| [[GfK Entertainment Charts|Top<br />100]]<br /><ref name=\"decharts\">{{cite web |url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/suche?artist_search=Ufo361&do_search=do |title=Suche Nach \"Ufo361\" |trans-title=Search after \"Ufo361\" |publisher=[[GfK Entertainment GmbH]] |accessdate=24 October 2018 |language=German}}</ref>\n! style=\"width:2.5em; font-size:85%\"| [[GfK Entertainment hip hop charts|Hip<br />hop]]<br /><ref name=\"hiphopdecharts\">For peak positions in Germany (Hip hop\u2013Charts):\n* {{cite web |url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/hiphop/for-date-1459461600000 |title=Offizielle Deutsche Charts \u2013 Top 20 Hiphop Charts 1. April 2016 (''Ich bin ein Berliner'') |trans-title=Official german charts \u2013 top 20 hip hop charts (''Ich bin ein Berliner'') |date=1 April 2016 |accessdate=24 October 2018 |publisher=[[GfK Entertainment GmbH]] |language=German}}\n* {{cite web |url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/hiphop/for-date-1475791200000 |title=Offizielle Deutsche Charts \u2013 Top 20 Hiphop Charts 7. Oktober 2016 (''Ich bin 2 Berliner'') |trans-title=Official german charts \u2013 top 20 hip hop charts (''Ich bin 2 Berliner'') |date=7 October 2016 |accessdate=24 October 2018 |publisher=[[GfK Entertainment GmbH]] |language=German}}\n* {{cite web |url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/hiphop/for-date-1493935200000 |title=Offizielle Deutsche Charts \u2013 Top 20 Hiphop Charts 5. Mai 2017 (''Ich bin