dits\"/>\n| title1   = Rather Be\n| note1    = featuring Jess Glynne\n| length1  = 3:48\n\n| title2   = Rather Be\n| note2    = featuring Jess Glynne) ([[The Magician (musician)|The Magician]] remix\n| length2  = 4:34\n\n| title3   = Rather Be\n| note3    = featuring Jess Glynne) (All About She remix\n| length3  = 3:49\n\n| title4   = Rather Be\n| note4    = featuring Jess Glynne) (Walter Ego remix\n| length4  = 5:57\n\n| title5   = Rather Be\n| note5    = featuring Jess Glynne) (Affelaye remix\n| length5  = 6:01\n}}\n\n==Credits and personnel==\n''Credits adapted from \"Rather Be\" CD single liner notes.''<ref name=\"credits\">{{cite AV media |people= [[Clean Bandit]] featuring [[Jess Glynne]] |year=2014 |title=Rather Be |medium=CD single |publisher=[[Warner Music Group|Warner Music Central Europe]] |id=825646317356}}</ref>\n\n===Musicians===\n{{colbegin}}\n* [[Jack Patterson (Clean Bandit)|Jack Patterson]] \u2013 keyboards, piano\n* [[Grace Chatto]] \u2013 cello\n* [[Luke Patterson (Clean Bandit)|Luke Patterson]] \u2013 drums\n* [[Anthony Strong]] \u2013 piano\n* Asher Zaccardelli \u2013 viola\n* Beatrice Philips \u2013 violin\n* [[Neil Amin-Smith]] \u2013 violin\n* [[Florence Rawlings]] \u2013 vocals\n* [[Jess Glynne]] \u2013 vocals\n{{colend}}\n\n===Technical===\n{{colbegin}}\n* [[Jack Patterson (Clean Bandit)|Jack Patterson]] \u2013 producer, mixer\n* [[Grace Chatto]] \u2013 producer\n* Lewis Hopkin \u2013 mastering\n* Wez Clarke \u2013 mixer\n* Liam Nolan \u2013 engineer\n* Brett Shaw \u2013 engineer (album version, mistakenly uncredited on single version)\n{{colend}}\n\n==Accolades==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! Year\n! Award\n! Nominated work\n! Category\n! Result\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"1\" | 2014\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[Billboard (magazine)|''Billboard''{{'}}s Best of 2014 Edition]]\n| \"Rather Be\"<ref name=\"billboard\"/>\n| 10 Best Songs of 2014\n| {{nominated|No. 4}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"  rowspan=\"1\" | 2